This is Perl module POSIX::pselect.

INSTALLATION

Install cpanm (App::cpanminus) and then run the following command to install
POSIX::pselect:

    $ cpanm POSIX::pselect

If you get an archive of this distribution, unpack it and build it
as per the usual:

    $ tar xzf POSIX-pselect-$version.tar.gz
    $ cd POSIX-pselect-$version
    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make && make test

Then install it:

    $ make install

DOCUMENTATION

POSIX::pselect documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    $ perldoc POSIX::pselect

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

